{"tid":2218451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"任達華、惠英紅將在國慶晚會上合唱《我的祖國》","createTime":"2020-09-26T08:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T10:18:53.000Z","uid":4203,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"061e9fe9208d0f77c1c5871abbbe53015295d4ed","tid":2218451,"uid":4203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:12:00.000Z","msg":"中共十一國慶將至，央視照慣例將舉辦國慶晚會，登場的台灣明星再度成為焦點，今日春晚官方微博公布9月30日國慶晚會陣容，其中多次高喊「我是中國人」的歐陽娜娜也在表演名單，她與任達華、惠英紅、杜江、童瑤、麥嘉欣、馬龍合唱開場曲《我的祖國》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nUVHmpx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnUVHmpx.jpg&h=129f2b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐陽娜娜身穿紅色禮服，受訪時表示，「大家一起合唱，又是一種特別澎湃的方式，覺得期待又激動，同時也挺興奮」。此外，<span class=\"red\">參與演出的台灣明星還包含在中國發展有成的張韶涵，她則是和陳偉霆、張碧晨、關曉彤、吳磊、Soler樂隊的夏利奧合唱抗疫歌曲《守護》，受訪時更獻上祝福「祝祖國繁榮昌盛」。</span>（吳佩蓁／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnrjoCL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnrjoCL.png&h=f6ed298b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全世界都減少慶祝活動 <br />\n得中國繼續大搞面子工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9877d06286316de696fb884d6c56ec19055e679","tid":2218451,"uid":5601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b34dc40ed3dbbef63939ebb79335bb1f9c2b6c8","tid":2218451,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"who？<br />\n啲過氣廢老明星我唔撚識<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d2bf4f59e4055672d2873871fd04f25cbeff6f","tid":2218451,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"張韶涵宜家咁撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces